        walkthrough = '1. Examine the Door:Merchant\'s House at (G-11) on the upper level behind Greyson in Lower Jeuno for a cutscene (HP #1).\nFrom this point on, you can complete the quest on any job\n2. Trade a piece of Mahogany Lumber to Osker near the chocobos and Brutus at (G-7) in Upper Jeuno.\n   - You will receive a Tamer\'s whistle, and be instructed to head to The Eldieme Necropolis.\n3. Zone into Batallia Downs from Beaucedine Glacier and enter The Eldieme Necropolis from the (F-5) entrance.\n   - This entrance can be reached quickly from Batallia Downs if you have the Lycopodium (NPC) warp unlocked.\n   - Voidwatch and/or Unity warps to Beaucedine Glacier are alternative methods to reach the (F-5) entrance quickly.\n4. Once inside, head to (D-4) and, if you are low level, clear the room before checking the north east sarcophagus.\n5. Examining the sarcophagus will spawn three NM\'s:\n   - 2 Tigers named Taifun and Trombe, and a hound named Sturm.\n   - Only Sturm needs to be defeated to proceed.\n   - The tigers can be charmed to help you in this fight.\n6. Once defeated examine the sarcophagus for a cutscene and your reward.',
