        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Vola to begin this quest with Monk as your main job.\n2. Exit the Tenshodo through the Door: "Neptune\'s Spire" to get a cutscene with Atori-Tutori.\n3. Obtain a Wyrm Beard from Nidhogg or Early Bird Catches the Wyrm.\n   - Trade the Wyrm Beard to the Door: "Neptune\'s Spire" for a cutscene.\n4. Speak to Degenhard, Bastok Markets (I-10).\n5. Obtain a Behemoth Tongue from King Behemoth or Horns of War.\n   - Trade the Behemoth Tongue to the Door: "Neptune\'s Spire" for another cutscene.\n6. Speak to Maat, Ru\'Lude Gardens (H-5).\n   - Obtain an Adamantoise Egg from Aspidochelone or The Hills Are Alive.\n   - Trade the Adamantoise Egg to the Door: "Neptune\'s Spire" for a cutscene.\n7. Finally, trade a Brown Belt to the same door for the final cutscene and a Black Belt.\n   - The Brown Belt is lost when trading it to the door.',
