        },
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to the Nomad Moogle in Ru\'Lude Gardens at (H-5).\n2. Trade 10 Kindred\'s Crests to the Nomad Moogle while also having 5 merit points.\n   - Keep in mind that besides obtaining seals from mobs, two easier ways exist to obtain various seals:\n     - Spend Login Campaign points - each seal is only 5 points.\n     - Shemo can exchange any other type of seal at a 3:1 ratio.\n3. Talk to the Nomad Moogle again. You will have to play a type of "Rock, Paper, Scissors", the goal is to win 5 rounds.\n   - "Raging Beast" beats "Silent Wind".\n   - "Silent Wind" beats "Soaring Dragon".\n   - "Soaring Dragon" beats "Raging Beast".\n   - This is all random, just pick options and hope to win.\n4. Should you lose the initial fight, the number of rounds you need to win in order to win the mini-game will decrease by 1. This will continue as you continue to lose rounds.\n5. Win at the mini-game and you will receive your reward.',
