        fame_level = nil,
        title = nil,
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = {'Blighted Gloom'},
        next = {'Mirror Images'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Luto for a cutscene.\n2. In Lower Jeuno, enter Neptune\'s Spire and examine the first door on the left for a cutscene.\n3. At the following locations you will need to call your Adventuring Fellow and use the proper HELM tool to retrieve the key items:\nNOTE: Warping back to town will cause your Fellow to disappear, forcing you to either wait out Signal Pearl\'s 6 hour cooldown or get a Tactics Pearl. Using Survival Guides does not make your Fellow vanish, so you can Guide to Maze of Shakhrami -> Guide to Jugner Forest -> Guide to West Sarutabaruta and run west to Giddeus with only one summon charge used. Alternatively, start at Giddeus via the Home Point or Domenic, and do the same thing in reverse. Mounts are safe to use without making your Fellow disappear.\n4. Once you have acquired all three key items, zone into Beaucedine Glacier for a cutscene, then head to the northernmost Mirror Pond at (J-7) for a cutscene.\n5. Return to Neptune\'s Spire and examine the door again for a cutscene, then speak to Luto to complete the quest.',
