        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Omer to begin this quest.\n2. The item Omer asks for drops off Krakens fished up in Qufim Island.\n   - No fishing skill is required to pull this up.\n3. Return the fishing rod to Omer for your reward.\n4. The game will freeze on the cutscene if you have your FPS set to 60. To set it to 30 with Windower use //config FrameRateDivisor 2',
