        previous = {'Researchers from the West'},
        next = {'Further Founts'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = 'After completing the previous quest and zoning out and back into Ru\'Lude Gardens, speak to Anastase and select the first option to expand the warp options.\nAt this point, you must discover eleven Geomagnetic Founts hidden throughout Vana\'diel by using the hints provided upon asking Anastase about his predictions:\n1. Using the Unity warp (content level 122) places you directly beside the zone entrance. Avoid dropping down after zoning out.\n2. Taking the survival guide will cut the distance in half compared to leaving from Windurst.\n3. Taking the survival guide to Gusgen Mines will get you there quickly.\n4. The Buburimu Peninsula survival guide will get you close.\nAfter attuning the Prototype attuner to each of the 11 geomagnetic founts above, return to Anastase to complete the quest.',
