        fame = nil,
        fame_level = nil,
        title = 'Destined Fellow',
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = {'Girl in the Looking Glass'},
        next = {'Past Reflections'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Note: You must zone after finishing Girl in the Looking Glass before you can start this quest.\n2. Speak to Luto Mewrilah for a cutscene.\n3. In Port San d\'Oria, head to Cargo Room B near Home Point #1 and speak to Portaure (H-9) for another cutscene that allows you to start a Burning Circle fight.\n   - Note: The battlefield applies a level cap of 40: recommend bringing level appropriate gear and food.\n   - The battlefield was designed to be soloable by players at level 30.\n   - Trust Magic can not be used.\n4. Go to Ghelsba Outpost and interact with the Hut Door (F/G-10) to enter the battlefield.\n5. The NM Carrion Dragon will spawn. Your Adventuring Fellow will arrive to assist you once you get it to around 80%.\n   - It has standard Dragon TP moves such as Thorn Song and Heavy Stomp. If you\'re unlucky it may use Petro Eyes and Petrify you or your fellow.\n6. Once the BC is complete you will receive a cutscene.\n7. Return to Luto to complete the quest and receive the reward.',
        notes = '1. Three people in a party may enter the BC at the same time, but it will spawn one Carrion Dragon for each one.\n2. Players who have already completed the quest will not be able to enter the battlefield.',
    },
