        previous = {'Path of the Bard'},
        next = {'The Requiem'},
        requirements = {
            {name = '[Key Item] Mertaire\'s bracelet', count = 1},
        },
        walkthrough = 'Speak with Mertaire at the Merry Minsterel Meadhouse in Lower Jeuno to begin the quest. You will receive [Key Item] Mertaire\'s bracelet.\n1. Travel to Ranguemont Pass and head to the pool at E-5.\n2. Activating the Waters of Oblivion will spawn the NM Tros.\n   - One NM pop will clear for multiple people if doing in a group.\n3. Click on the Waters of Oblivion once Tros is defeated for a cutscene. At the conclusion of the cutscene you will receive your Paper Knife.\nYou do not need to be on Bard to activate the Waters of Oblivion, only that you have [Key Item] Mertaire\'s bracelet. Therefore, if you have a higher level job you can switch to that job and defeat Tros easily.',
