        reward = 'Increases Familiarity Limit to 50.',
        fame = nil,
        fame_level = nil,
        title = nil,
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = {'Mirror, Mirror'},
        next = {'Blighted Gloom'},
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Zone after the previous quest. Speak to Luto for a cutscene that begins this quest. (If you receive a conversation about Fellow Points, speak to her again.) She will ask you to retrieve a book from the Optistery.\n2. Go to Windurst Waters (Home Point #1) and speak to Tosuka-Porika at (Northern, G-8) for a brief cutscene.\n3. In the cutscene you will be requested to gather the following food:\n4. Level 65 Cooking recipe\n5. Auction House/Bazaar\n6. Bernegeois - Eastern Adoulin (G-8) 2,772 gil\n7. Shilah - Southern San d\'Oria (K-6) 2,494 - 3,049 gil (First place in conquest, citizens only)\n8. Yoskolo - Lower Jeuno (H-8) 5,544 gil\n9. Boncort - Northern San d\'Oria (F-8) 180 - 220 gil (First/Second place in conquest)\n10. Chomo Jinjahl - Windurst Waters (Northern, E-8) 140 - 976 gil (not automatically restocked)\n11. Croumangue - Port San d\'Oria (G-7) 180 - 220 gil (First/Second place in conquest)\n12. Defliaa - Western Adoulin (I-11) 200 gil\n13. Glyke - Upper Jeuno (F-7) inside the Marble Bridge, 200 gil\n14. Kopopo - Windurst Waters (Northern, E-8) 140 - 976 gil (not automatically restocked)\n15. Shilah - Southern San d\'Oria (K-6) 180 - 220 gil (First/Second place in conquest)\n16. Taajiji - Windurst Waters (Northern, F-10) 5,932 - 7,251 gil (First/Second place in conquest)\n17. Glyke - Upper Jeuno (F-7) 1,860 gil\n18. Taajiji - Windurst Waters (Northern, F-10) 1,674 - 2,046 gil\n19. Trade those six food to Tosuka-Porika for a cutscene.\n   - (You\'ll receive "Looking Glass Legends", but it\'s neither an item nor a key item, just mentioned in the text during the quest.)\n20. Return to Upper Jeuno and speak to Luto for a cutscene.\n21. Speak to Khumo Daramasteh at Port Jeuno (J-8) (Home Point #1) for a cutscene that completes the quest.',
