        walkthrough = '1. (Optional): Speak to Collet near the clock tower (G-7) for gossip.\n2. Speak to Derrick in Lower Jeuno\'s Chamber of Commerce and Industry (H-7) and ask to start a petition.\n3. To complete the quest, you will need to trade the Tower Petition to 10 NPCs. Their locations are:\n   - Pitantimand - Port Jeuno (H-7)\n   - Teigero-Bangero - Lower Jeuno (H-10)\n   - Zauko - Lower Jeuno (I-6)\n   - Baudin - Upper Jeuno (G-8)\n   - Collet - Upper Jeuno (G-7)\n   - Constance - Upper Jeuno (G-9)\n   - Monberaux - Upper Jeuno (G-10)\n   - Souren - Upper Jeuno (G-9)\n   - Zuber - Upper Jeuno (F-7) (inside the Marble Bridge Tavern)\n   - Radeivepart - Ru\'Lude Gardens (H-9)\n4. Once you have all 10 signatures trade the Tower Petition to Derrick to complete the quest.',
