        },
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Brutus at (G-7) in Upper Jeuno who will give you three Aquaflora Key Items.\nYou can be on any job from here on.\n2. Examine the pools on map 2 of Fei\'Yin located at (H-8), (H-5) and lastly (F-5). They are the little green marks on the map.\n   - Home Point #2 is the closest warp just outside of the Cloister of Frost\n3. When the pool located at (F-5) is inspected an NM named Dabotz\'s Ghost will spawn. The ghost can actually spawn at any pool but it seems (F-5) was only available after the other 2 were used.\n   - Dabotz\'s Ghost is a Black Mage and can cast various Black Magic spells including Tornado.\n   - Dabotz\'s Ghost uses curse often.\n   - Take off Sneak if you have it on, he will spawn in the water of the pool and you can\'t get to him unless he aggros you.\n4. After defeating Dabotz\'s Ghost, check the pool at (F-5) again.\n5. Return to Brutus for a cutscene.\n6. Next head to Castle Oztroja and kill the monsters to find an Oztroja Chest Key.\n   - Alternatively, you can purchase one from the Curio Vendor Moogle.\n7. Use the key to open a chest inside the castle to receive a Beast Collar.\n8. Trade the Beast Collar to the Opo-opo NPC Tebhi.\n   - Tebhi likes to roam the indoor pond that is near the brass door to the magicite for city missions.\n   - Tebhi will dissapear for 3 minutes after accepting the Beast Collar.\n9. Return to Brutus for your reward.',
