        walkthrough = '1. After finishing all of the cutscenes after Dawn including Blueblade Fell, walk towards the Palace in Ru\'Lude Gardens to begin the cutscene.\n2. Examine the Dilapidated Gate in Misareaux Coast (F-7) for a cutscene.\n   - The Unity Warp npc-option "content level 122" > Misareaux Coast puts you right in front of this gate.\n3. Head to the Unstable Displacement in the northwest section of Riverne - Site #B01 (E-7) for a cutscene.\n   - The Unstable Displacement will not turn green until you are standing almost directly on top of it.\n   - (Fastest Route) Use Home Point > Riverne - Site #B01.\n     - If using the Home Point go northeast to the normal Spatial Displacement in order to reach the island that has the green displacement.\n   - (Optional) - You can take the long way from the Dilapidated Gate in Misareaux Coast (F-7) to get there using Giant Scale along the way to reach (E-7).\n4. Click the green Unstable Displacement again after the cutscene to enter the BC Storms of Fate with Bahamut.\n5. Kill Bahamut for another cutscene.\n6. Return to the Palace in Ru\'Lude Gardens for a cutscene that completes the quest.',
