        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Mertaire in Lower Jeuno, who tells you to take the Star ring (tarnished) to an antique collector.\n   - Quest wont be listed in log yet.\n2. Speak to Imasuke (E-6) in Port Jeuno.\n   - You must have your current job set to Bard to receive the cutscene.\n   - After speaking with him, you may change to any job.\n3. Travel to (I-10) in Xarcabard and examine the Perennial Snow at the end of the short tunnel.\n   - You must now wait one Earth minute before you can retrieve the ring.\n4. Retrieve the Star ring (indecipherable) by examining the Perennial Snow.\n5. Go back to Imasuke who tells you to find someone who can translate the ring.\n6. Head to Chateau d\'Oraguille and speak to Chalvatot at (F-7) to receive the Moon ring.\n7. Listen to his instructions and travel to Monastic Cavern via Davoi @ (H-11)\n8. Walk to the small circular room at (I-8) with the altar in it\n   - Be careful of the True Sight Orcish Warlord that roams the area\n9. After clearing the Orcs, examine the altar to spawn Bugaboo\n10. Defeat him, then examine the altar again for a cutscene.\n11. Return and speak to Chalvatot for your reward, and to complete the quest.',
        notes = nil,
    },
