        fame_level = nil,
        title = nil,
        repeatable = nil,
        previous = {'A Trial in Tandem, Redux'},
        next = {'A Quaternary Trial in Tandem'},
        requirements = {
            {name = '[Key Item] Magian trial log', count = 1},
        },
        walkthrough = '1. Speak with Luto Mewrilah for a cutscene that begins the quest and provides the [Key Item] Magian Mooglehood missive.\n2. Speak to the Magian Moogle in Ru\'Lude Gardens at (H-5) for a cutscene and a Tandem Necklace +2.\n3. Trade the Tandem Necklace +2 to the Magian Moogle (Blue) in Ru\'Lude Gardens at (H-5) to start Magian Trial 4446.\n4. Your Adventuring Fellow must Weapon Skill any type of monster that give XP to your Adventuring Fellow 20 times while you wear the Tandem Necklace +2.\n   - Weapon Skills must hit in order to count.\n   - Set your Adventuring Fellow to Fierce Attacker for this quest, and do not equip your Adventuring Fellow with a club, in order to avoid Moonlight and Starlight. Moonlight and Starlight do not count for Magian Trial 4446.\n5. After your Adventuring Fellow Weapon Skills 20 times, trade the Tandem Necklace +2 to the Magian Moogle (Blue) to receive a Mythril Meed.\n6. Trade the Mythril Meed to Luto Mewrilah to complete the quest.',
        notes = '1. Weapons in Ro\'Maeve had decent HP for the Adventuring Fellow to build TP and WS.\n   - Weapons are not too far from the Survival Guide\n2. Bring a Red Mage and use: Distract, Paralyze, Slow, Addle, Blind.',
